{
  "stem": "20035.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we marched towards the camp, which wasn't further than maybe two miles from the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the reason why I mentioned the twin camp, the [GERMAN], was immediately adjacent to our camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had a full view of what's happening there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, to describe the camp, I don't think so that you want I should describe it to you, how the campus basically was built as a-- Birkenau, where we went, that camp was originally-- all the barracks were prefabricated horse barns.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I can tell you only that I was in Barrack 21, in Camp B.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And immediately adjacent to us was-- was the [GERMAN], the twin lager.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was 20 if memory was-- I think so it's 22-- 23 barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One was the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So 22 barracks were living, people, there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barracks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "22 individual--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Housing unit, or this-- this-- these horse barns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I would like to say that our-- well, we were 922 in ours, 21.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "921, in Barack 21.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were ushered in, it was already sundown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To try to describe the amount of room, what we had, we had to put the hand on the shoulder once again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Line of fives, each side of the barrack, line of fives, marching in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then put the hand on the shoulder of the guy in front of you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then elbow to elbow-- elbow was a lot to put, you know, on your hip.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And elbow to elbow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then both ends of the barracks, there was one bulb, one-- one light, one bulb.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the bulb went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And somebody else, when we later realized he's our kapo, that he's the one who is in charge of the-- of that barrack, to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
